file.name: tag-clash-merged.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: "Merged documentation"
  version: "1.0"
paths:
  "/testA":
    get:
      tags:
       - a
       - b
       - c
       - d
      responses:
        202:
          description: "success"
  "/testB":
    get:
      tags:
       - a1
       - b1
       - c
       - e
      responses:
        202:
          description: "success"
tags:
  - name: a
    description: description of a
    externalDocs:
      url: http://example.org/docs/a
      description: Reference
  - name: b
    description: description of b
  - name: a1
    description: testB description of a
    externalDocs:
      url: http://example.org/docs/a
      description: Reference
  - name: b1
    description: testB description of b
